snippet.title: Warframe | Fortuna Official Update Trailer - Out Now on PC #LiftTogether
snippet.description:
Welcome to Fortuna, Outworlder. Explore the frigid landscape of Venus populated with new Corpus threats, subterranean mysteries and an ecosystem on the brink of destruction. 

Available now on PC - coming soon to consoles. Learn more: https://warframe.com/fortuna/info
